Alur Kerja

1. Buat repo di GitHub
        ↓
2. Clone ke komputer (git clone)
        ↓
3. Buat branch baru (git checkout -b)
        ↓
4. Edit file / tambah kode
        ↓
5. git add .
        ↓
6. git commit -m "pesan"
        ↓
7. git push
        ↓
8. Buat Pull Request di GitHub
        ↓
9. Review → Merge ke main

Alur Perubahan Simbolnya

File baru dibuat      →  U  (Untracked)
        ↓
   git add .          →  A  (Added/Staged)
        ↓
  git commit          →  (simbol hilang, sudah tersimpan)
        ↓
  Edit file lagi      →  M  (Modified)
        ↓
   git add .          →  A  (Added/Staged)
        ↓
  git commit          →  (simbol hilang lagi)